text: Kamyshovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kamyshovsky Selsoviet, Limansky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 654 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 100 km from Astrakhan, 37 km from Liman. == References == Category:Rural localities in Limansky District
title: Kamyshovo
